title: Man Goes For Morning Dip in Gonorrhea-Infected Canal Once Again
text:
Man Goes For Morning Dip in Gonorrhea-Infected Canal Once Again 
Published By: Gawker.com - Today 
Last time Christopher Swain swam the waters of Brooklyn’s Gowanus Canal, he didn’t contact gonorrhea. The second time’s the charm, tho...
